{
  "stem": "25423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I was stationed near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a gymnasium, and I went to this fine lady, who was a director of the gymnasium, told her that I am a Pole from Lwow, and I couldn't finish my schooling, and I would like to get a degree, and how to go about it.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, she said, you can sit down to an examination as an external student.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will test you and see whether you can do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there for almost two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the teachers were very kind because they worked with me on what I do, subjects, prepared me for the examination.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I sit down, and I passed it, and I have a certificate, which is a baccalaureate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And your certificate is as Roman Matkowski?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Roman Matkowski.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I just watched it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't function in Poland as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I smuggled these two priests out of Poland illegally to Czechoslovakia and from there to Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We traveled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I described it in the book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, certainly, because we could be caught by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once we crossed the Russian demarcation line, there was no risk anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would assume today looking, I didn't know, precisely, but I think that there must have been some underground organization guided by the Haganah people in Europe, which was called Bricha.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they organized the transports of Jews-- men, women, and children-- westward from Poland to Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forged Jewish papers for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I became Kurt Lewin the minute I left the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no need to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a complicated question.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had on several occasions some problems to prove my identity.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
